document_data.name: Dendever Street
document_data.mainbody: '''Dendever Street''' was found in the town of [[New Velar|Harrowdale]].
document_data.Description: Dendever Street began on its north side branching from [[Lancegallop Lane]]. The road passed south and southwest through the town terminating on the [[Heart of the Harbor]] pier just offshore on the [[Dragon Reach]].
